title: 😺Discord Instead of Telegram
body:
Do you think it would be better to make the YSL.IO Discord (https://discord.com/invite/ysl-io) the main place to go for conversation/technical support/price discussion?

This means Telegram will only be used for YSL.IO announcements.
author: 0x03fBc53527B534De379105fB35dDEf765eFE76FD
